ach side. A value of 0 produces no buffer. A value of 512 produces a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"buffer as wide as the tile itself. Larger values produce fewer rendering"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"artifacts near tile edges and slower performance. The default value is 128."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionbuffer","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection"}}}